text: Anatoly Stepanenko (born 23 August 1949) is a Soviet former cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Soviet Union Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
